Intro data grid. Send all tx events from existing db to new data grid
new command service for write API

Create new UI (write) to new service via strangler API
Migrate tx events from existing service to new data grid
Keep existing system updated by populating with events from data grid. Legacy system will serve as fallback to mitigate risk
Multi version app become possible
